issue.title: [CF 1566] Diminishing Returns Tracker: Psychic Horror misplaced.
issue.body:
The priest talent "Psychic Horror" is categorized as an incap in TMW's DR tracker. It's actually a stun and DRs other stuns.


> Posted by CurseForge user InzaneMode | Imported from CurseForge issue #1566 | Raw
